name: MSRI-QUADRO-GIFPOGV-YW-01
description: v4w.enko - "MSRI-QUADRO-GIFPOGV-YW-01" is a gif animation of  3d Object, generated with custom definition. 4 lofts are animated in 4 layers for each color: Pink , Orange, Green, Violet. The cells of the Yellow "3d voronoi" cube are linked to the attractor`s points of the lofts. Another one group of cells linked to the same attractor points  are rotating as the white cube .  The parallel projections are showing the different viewpoints of the same form. Left, Front, Top, Bottom. Total 64 frames, 1024*1024px canvas.
